<br>
<br>
Combine the Ink and the Rune in a fletching kit to make a Velium Etched Rune. (Fletching trivial 19<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
Show this rune to Talem Tucter in the Jewelry Shop. He will give you a pattern. Combine the pattern, 2 bars of platinum, and a <br>
small piece of Velium in a jeweler's kit to make The Casing. (Jewelry trivial at 182)<br>
<br>
<br>
Combine the casing and your rune in a jeweler's kit to make an Encased Velium Etched Rune. (Jewelry trivial at 182)<br>
<br>
<br>
Combine the Encased Velium Etched Rune and your shawl and the pattern you got at the beginning of this process in a tailoring<br>
 kit to make THE SEVENTH SHAWL (Trivial at Tailoring 212)<br>
<br>
<br>
